refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public ZMQCert::save stringfilename
Saves the full certificate (public and secret keys) to disk. This writes the public key to filename and the secret key to a companion file with a _secret suffix. Added in ZMQ extension version 1.1.3.

&reftitle.parameters;


  filename

   The path of the public certificate file to write.
